INSTAWASH - DELIVERING PREMIUM SHINE TO YOUR WHEELS.

INSTAWASH gives you the opportunity to get premium car detailing by certified pro-detailers without having to travel to a car wash and wait for your turn. It is premium service at any time and anywhere for your convenience.

- Our instant wash function gives you the chance to request our service right here and now to fit your plans.
- With our reservation function you have the opportunity to schedule our service at any time that fit your needs.

- Our Premium Detailing Products

- We use the best quality products to provided a premium standard of detailing to cover the everyday needs of a car owner. From the professional detailing team trained for our services, to our custom made microfiber towels and premium products used for the detailing. We take pride in every detail to ensure the INSTAWASH experience is a spotless one.

- Our Professional Detailers

Every detailers at INSTAWASH must go through our professional detailing training program. This program is to ensure that detailers provide a premium standard service. Only once they passed the training program will be allowed to detail your car.

“When you need a car wash, Instawash will visit you.”

Instawash is the No. 1 premium on-demand car wash platform, and is the only real-time order matching service in Korea.

Premium door-to-door car wash service is provided so that customers can conveniently use high-quality services anytime, anywhere.

If you apply for the service through the app, the professional technician will go to the parked location in time for the car wash and carry out the service.

The service with the highest customer satisfaction rating as the number one car wash service:

- Only technicians who have completed an average of 100 hours of IPAA (Instawash Professional Auto care Academy) training course provide on-site service.

- We provide the best service from 46 steps of manual car wash order and copper line & hand motion for the best quality.

- We provide Ater-sales service reflecting 100% customer satisfaction policy in case of service dissatisfaction within 24 hours

*INSTAWASH provides the only real-time and pre-order car wash service in Korea.
- You can get service from the nearest technician through real-time car wash, and choose the time of your choice through Instawash's unique reservation system.

*Based on the advanced technology and service quality of INSTAWASH, B2B in various areas is conducted.
- Strategic alliance with automotive and lifestyle conglomerate brands
We have strategic partnerships with various brands such as automobiles and lifestyle brands (Hyundai Motors, Kia Motors, Genesis, Hyundai Hillstate, Lotte Card, BMW, Maserati, Jaguar, Land Rover, iParking, Daeyoung Chaevi).

* INSTAWASH uses premium car wash products.
- The best car wash products made in the US and Switzerland are selected and used after testing. In addition, to ensure the best car wash quality, all car wash kits are thoroughly managed by the headquarters, and all microfiber towels are collected at head office in batches after one use in order to prevent fine scratches and contaminants, and contaminated towels are not reused.

* INSTAWASH provides guaranteed quality.
- No matter which technician of Instawash receives car washing service order, only technicians who have completed IPAA expert courses are on-site to provide standardized high-quality service, maintaining industry-leading customer satisfaction.
